<p>2. I like to avoid using the word "Vegan" when describing plant based food in Thailand. "Jay" is our local term for the same concept, and it's much older and also has a lot less political baggage and judgement associated with it. Much more accessible I think 👍<br>
<br>
Ok onto the food!</p>
